{"tid":160281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］有個朋友跌左落海可以點做","createTime":"2017-03-17T14:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T17:04:18.000Z","uid":84798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf82310cddfc4daf5684d4fe3c94f933b140d31","tid":160281,"uid":84798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我有個朋友越來越沉迷個啲網上group，睇見你明知個啲group係專比狗公搵食同埋娘娘收兵，其實越來越擔心你，認真同你講你又話只係食下花生唔會有事，我只係怕你繼續沉迷玩出火。<br />\n<br />\n係高登連登入下group識朋友其實真係無問題，因為包括自己都有入一啲group傾下計交流下識下朋友，甚至有唔少巴絲既另一半都係因為咁樣既途徑而認識，所以我唔覺得網上識朋友甚至識另一半係有問題。不過咩地方都總會有壞人，唔好咁易相信人，唔係到頭來受傷既只會係自己，宜家無事唔代表之後唔會出事，無論男定女都係。<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲有無相似既經驗，可以係度分享下，另外希望大家幫手推比我個朋友睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17c8d807adda34e403a9965304bb3809e161560","tid":160281,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"唉濕撚晒唉唔撚驚"},{"pid":"88ca76df70fca976162c28b7f937ff4e0d283a4d","tid":160281,"uid":84798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e801c3b3cd53bc57ad94891032319a3964474f1","tid":160281,"uid":84798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d3fb0157e1d1286a29cd6b8271b9fb3a0fb713","tid":160281,"uid":84798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa77cea0529fe7ef4834aac12ce0b7ba51f8b0b","tid":160281,"uid":84798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm